    "date": "2005-08-02T14:30:06Z",
    "text": "Bond Financing Renewal Act of 2005 - Amends the Internal Revenue Code to: (1) accelerate to FY2007 (from FY2010) the $10 million issuance increase for qualified small-issue bonds; and (2) allow a tax deduction for interest expense on qualified small-issue bonds with an aggregate authorized face amount of less than $2 million."
